215
00:20:20,579 --> 00:20:23,920
[SPEAKER_36]: Learning a language fosters values of communication and inclusion.

216
00:20:24,100 --> 00:20:28,641
[SPEAKER_36]: And for me personally, it's helped me appreciate the extraordinary diversity of the world we live in.

