00:21:04,188 --> 00:21:11,894
[SPEAKER_34]: Hi, I'm Sophie Levine from the Andrews and through learning about languages we can have a more inclusive school environment and a greater sense of community.

224
00:21:12,434 --> 00:21:16,977
