01:36:55,922 --> 01:36:59,424
[SPEAKER_32]: And then my last one, STEM.

851
01:36:59,524 --> 01:37:08,912
[SPEAKER_32]: Just because there is not a STEM specialist called out for the Missituck and the McGlynn, that does not mean that there is not structured STEM at those two schools.

