[SPEAKER_06]: I mean we work with our partners in Belmont and in Maynard.

908
01:43:20,940 --> 01:43:34,052
[SPEAKER_06]: on a daily basis, and I will tell you that, especially as you get into spaces that are more used heavily for sports, that becomes a very difficult prioritization decision.

909
01:43:34,512 --> 01:43:42,439
[SPEAKER_06]: And I would say building in the management capacity, the administrative capacity of the site director and the managing director,

910
01:43:43,119 --> 01:43:56,940
[SPEAKER_06]: is the way that you're able to have those conversations with school leadership and with other district leaders to make sure that we're understanding the full needs of that school building and the different spaces and how it's going to impact

