[SPEAKER_06]: Because out of all of the schools, it is the most limited for outside play.

927
01:46:14,963 --> 01:46:18,244
[SPEAKER_06]: And if we're talking about it being the second largest in terms of needs,

928
01:46:19,044 --> 01:46:22,827
[SPEAKER_06]: to only have really one good outdoor programming space.

929
01:46:22,847 --> 01:46:45,865
[SPEAKER_06]: That was part of the reason why we highlighted the Roberts in our mock schedule for all of you, even though there's multiple versions to look at in the full report, is because it takes some coordination in the schedule just to really even meet the needs for the after school students, much less any folks, community folks who are using the playground or to get something like a pickup soccer game organized.

