01:47:01,233 --> 01:47:05,556
[SPEAKER_14]: So throughout the year of this review and our work with basic.

934
01:47:05,657 --> 01:47:12,522
[SPEAKER_14]: So everyone is very clear on what it's going to take in order to meet these expectations.

