1180
02:10:24,459 --> 02:10:25,280
[SPEAKER_07]: No, that's wonderful to hear.

1181
02:10:25,740 --> 02:10:30,564
[SPEAKER_07]: And I think something that you both mentioned that I think is a part of this is also this idea of fairness, right?

1182
02:10:30,584 --> 02:10:35,488
