1233
02:16:16,091 --> 02:16:26,260
[SPEAKER_06]: the survey, particularly where the wait list students who are currently, you know, kind of waiting on the wait list are, that the need is absolutely at those schools.

1234
02:16:26,800 --> 02:16:31,704
[SPEAKER_06]: So as far as next year, again, the piece that Michael talked about earlier with

1235
02:16:32,565 --> 02:16:41,432
[SPEAKER_06]: And what needs to happen programmatically, what needs to happen structurally within the program, how we use the spaces, nothing needs to change.

1236
02:16:42,453 --> 02:16:44,314
[SPEAKER_06]: I can't say nothing needs to change.

1237
02:16:44,514 --> 02:16:51,640
[SPEAKER_06]: We need to utilize, we need to use those spaces differently, but we don't need to use any more spaces in either one of those schools for next year.

1238
02:16:52,417 --> 02:17:07,766
[SPEAKER_06]: Now, if the Brooks does grow to a place where it's serving 300 students per day, you know, 330 students per day, 340 students per day, we may have to look at using additional classrooms for that type of program.

1239
02:17:08,186 --> 02:17:11,608
[SPEAKER_06]: I will say that our largest program, which

1240
