02:34:07,755 --> 02:34:08,516
[SPEAKER_29]: Do you want to?

1426
02:34:08,696 --> 02:34:09,677
[SPEAKER_29]: I mean, Christine.

1427
02:34:09,737 --> 02:34:10,437
[SPEAKER_29]: I have a question.

1428
02:34:15,978 --> 02:34:23,503
[SPEAKER_20]: How much effort did you put in to try and interview with kids and families?

